    <para><emphasis role="bold">Description:</emphasis> The <userinput>value-pairs()</userinput> option creates structured name-value pairs from the data and metadata of the log message. For details on using <userinput>value-pairs()</userinput>, see <xref linkend="concepts-value-pairs"/>.</para>
    <note>
        <para>Empty keys are not logged.</para>
